  "answer": "Both construction permits and code violations have seen significant drops compared to last year. Permits decreased by 92.4% to 96.9%, with counts falling from 54,817 to as low as 1,696. Similarly, code violations dropped by 91.9% to 96.1%, with totals declining from 25,384 to as low as 981. These represent dramatic reductions in both categories.",
